import sys

N = int(input())
A = int(input())
B = int(input())
C = int(input())
D = int(input())
E = int(input())

i = 0
n = N
while n > 0:
    if i % 5 == 0:
        n -= min(n, A)
    elif i % 5 == 1:
        n -= min(n, B)
    elif i % 5 == 2:
        n -= min(n, C)
    elif i % 5 == 3:
        n -= min(n, D)
    else:
        n -= min(n, E)
    i += 1

print(i)
